{% call foundations.section("Theme") -%}

  <p>The choice of which theme to apply is based on content and user experience needs.</p>

  <h4 class="margin-top--8">Light theme</h4>

  <p>The light theme is the default theme. It is designed for simplicity and accessibility while allowing UI elements to be distinguished from each other.</p>

  <div class="margin-top--4">
    {% call foundations.example(palette='lightest') %}
